  • org.glassfish.jersey.tests.memleaks.redeployment:redeployment-hello-world-app-ref:jar:2.22
    jersey-tests-memleak-redeployment-hello-world-app-ref

    Description: Maven module that tests :helloworld-webapp:war in order to prevent regression of a problem where a repetitive redeployment may have caused memory leaks. To run this test, execute from Jersey root dir: [1] Glassfish: mvn install -am -pl :redeployment-hello-world-app-ref -P gf4,memleak-redeployment [2] Weblogic: mvn install -am -pl :redeployment-hello-world-app-ref -P wls,memleak-redeployment [3] Tomcat: mvn install -am -pl :redeployment-hello-world-app-ref -P tomcat,memleak-redeployment

    URL: https://jersey.github.io/project/project/project/redeployment-hello-world-app-ref/
